#1. Create a greeting for your program.
print("Welcome to the Great 100 Days of Code Band Name Generator!")

#2. Ask the user for the city that they grew up in.
hometown = input("What's the name of the town where you grew up? \n")

#3. Ask the user for the name of a pet.
pet = input("What was your childhood pet's name? \n")

#4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.
print("\nYour official punk rock band name is: \n" + hometown + " " + pet +"!")

